OL,3,CJewish community ambulances set on
OL,4,Cfire in antisemitic arson attack
OL,6,FSangeeta Kandola reports for Good
OL,7,FMorning Britain from Golders Green,
OL,8,FNorth London, where the suspected
OL,9,Farson took place
OL,11,FPolice are investigating a suspected
OL,12,Fantisemitic arson attack in North
OL,13,FLondon after four ambulances belonging
OL,14,Fto a Jewish Community Ambulance
OL,15,Fservice were set alight.
OL,17,FSix fire engines and 40 firefighters
OL,18,Fwere called to Highfield Road, in
OL,19,FGolders Green, during the early hours
OL,20,Fof Monday morning and found four
OL,21,FHatzalah ambulances on fire.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,318,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31702
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1774357890
OL,3,CJewish community ambulances set on
OL,4,Cfire in antisemitic arson attack
OL,6,FMultiple cylinders on the vehicles had
OL,7,Fexploded during the fire, causing
OL,8,Fwindows to break in an adjacent block
OL,9,Fof flats.
OL,11,FNo injuries were reported and the
OL,12,Fincident is being treated as an
OL,13,Fantisemitic hate crime, the Met Police
OL,14,Fsaid.
OL,16,FOfficers believe three people were
OL,17,Finvolved in the fire.
OL,19,F"We are in the process of examining
OL,20,FCCTV and are aware of online footage,"
OL,21,FSuperintendent Sarah Jackson said.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,318,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1774357890
OL,3,CJewish community ambulances set on
OL,4,Cfire in antisemitic arson attack
OL,6,F"We believe we are looking for three
OL,7,Fsuspects at this early stage.
OL,9,F"There have been no arrests yet, and
OL,10,Fwe would urge anyone with information
OL,11,Fto please contact us as soon as
OL,12,Fpossible - you can do so anonymously
OL,13,Fif you wish."
OL,15,FPolice will be engaging with faith
OL,16,Fleaders and carrying out additional
OL,17,Fpatrols in the area while the
OL,18,Finvestigation continues,
OL,19,FSuperintendent Jackson said.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/7
