OL,3,CJewish community ambulances set on
OL,4,Cfire in antisemitic arson attack
OL,6,FThe fire was under control just after
OL,7,F3am, the London Fire Brigade service
OL,8,Fsaid, while police remained at the
OL,9,Fscene on Monday morning.
OL,11,FSubscribe for free to our weekly
OL,12,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,13,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,14,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,16,FHatzola is a non-profit, volunteer
OL,17,Forganisation, which provides hospital
OL,18,Ftransportation and emergency care for
OL,19,Fthe local community regardless of
OL,20,Ftheir religion.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/7
