OL,3,CJewish community ambulances set on
OL,4,Cfire in antisemitic arson attack
OL,6,FThe service is a short walk from the
OL,7,FNorth Western Reform Synagogue
OL,8,F(Alyth), which marked its 90th
OL,9,Fanniversary in 2023.
OL,11,F"This is a deeply shocking antisemitic
OL,12,Farson attack," Prime Minister Sir Keir
OL,13,FStarmer said in a statement on social
OL,14,Fmedia.
OL,16,F"My thoughts are with the Jewish
OL,17,Fcommunity who are waking up this
OL,18,Fmorning to this horrific news.
OL,19,FAntisemitism has no place in our
OL,20,Fsociety."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
