OL,3,CJewish community ambulances set on
OL,4,Cfire in antisemitic arson attack
OL,6,FHe added: "Anyone with any information
OL,7,Fmust come forward to the police".
OL,9,FShomrim, a non-profit organisation
OL,10,Fwhich operates a neighborhood watch in
OL,11,Fthe area, condemned the attack this
OL,12,Fmorning on social media.
OL,14,F"This was not only a criminal act of
OL,15,Farson, but a targeted and deeply
OL,16,Fconcerning incident affecting a vital
OL,17,Femergency service serving the local
OL,18,FJewish community," it said in a post
OL,19,Fon X.
