OL,3,CJewish community ambulances set on
OL,4,Cfire in antisemitic arson attack
OL,6,FThe number of antisemitic incidents
OL,7,Freported across the UK has risen since
OL,8,Flate 2023, according to the Community
OL,9,FSecurity Trust, which works to protect
OL,10,Fthe Jewish community, with 3,700
OL,11,Frecorded in 2025, up from 1,662 in
OL,12,F2022.
